# Hermetic env for the test suite — intentionally empty.
#
# The `pytest-dotenv` plugin (when installed) auto-loads a .env into os.environ
# at startup. pyproject.toml points it here instead of the project .env so a
# developer's real credentials (SLACK_SIGNING_SECRET, GMAIL_PUBSUB_TOKEN, …)
# never leak into tests and flip connectors out of their dev-mode defaults.
